Package: dispPO
Title: Visualize PegelOnline water level data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Felix", "Op de Hipt", , "felixodh85@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Displays pegelonline water level data. 
  It shows the current station status (online/offline) and the current
  water level status as published by pegelonline.de. Provides functions to fetch, process, and visualize water level measurements
    from the PegelOnline API. Includes caching, status calculation, and Leaflet map integration.
